Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.22,Staff,,0,0,0,,This SUB is presented by Baidu RWBY Bar\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NCreator: sbz_kid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:20.50,D,,0,0,0,,The world of Remnant is a dangerous place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:23.57,D,,0,0,0,,Particularly for man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:30.41,D,,0,0,0,,In the countless years that humanity has roamed the planet, civilizations have grown and fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.91,D,,0,0,0,,But four have withstood the test of time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.18,D,,0,0,0,,Atlas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.52,D,,0,0,0,,Mistral
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:37.95,D,,0,0,0,,Vacuo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:39.08,D,,0,0,0,,Vale
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:47.30,D,,0,0,0,,These four kingdoms with the help of natural barriers and human tenacity, have proven that they have the will to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:52.26,D,,0,0,0,,Each kingdom has a governing council to represent the people and their needs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.04,D,,0,0,0,,Next, comes the military
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:58.08,D,,0,0,0,,While most kingdoms only call on its citizens to serve when needed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.14,D,,0,0,0,,others find it important to be..prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:06.62,D,,0,0,0,,There are still those who choose to venture outside the walls of the kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:10.36,D,,0,0,0,,Roaming nomads and small villages are not uncommon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:15.49,D,,0,0,0,,Yet neither is their tendency to..disappear, overnight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.99,D,,0,0,0,,Lastly, the Huntsmen academies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:25.00,D,,0,0,0,,These institutions' soul purpose is to train the next generation of huntsmen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:32.57,D,,0,0,0,,The next generation of defenders that will live and die to protect the lifestyle that they've become so accustomed to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:36.94,D,,0,0,0,,Yes, the world of Remnant is indeed a dangerous place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:40.48,D,,0,0,0,,But the four kingdoms stand as beacons of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.95,D,,0,0,0,,As safe havens from the darkness that surrounds them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:47.49,D,,0,0,0,,They are the key to mankind's survival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:51.52,D,,0,0,0,,as long as they stand united..
